title: Presenting Alt.Latino: The rapper Farruko on finding God — and a whole new sound
description: From our friends at Alt.Latino, Felix Contreras and Anamaria Sayre sit down with Carlos Efrén Reyes Rosado to talk about creating the character of Farruko, developing a relationship with God and spreading a message of love.
